    <div class="ERNCBanner-Content-BG">
        <div class="ERNCBanner-Content">
            <div class="Content-Title">
                <span>Empyreal Nucleus (ERNC)</span>
            </div>
            <div class="Content-Text">ERNC is an ERC20-based governance money for the PonPonSnake universe. Holders can
                participate in
                game decision-making and voting, and also gain high-level game items. It is the PonPonSnake community's
                most valuable trade asset.
            </div>
        </div>

