<div class="ERNC-Card">
    <div class="ERNC-Card-All">

        <div class="Card-BG">
            <div class="Card-Inner">

                <div class="IconBlock">
                    <div class="IconBlock-Img">
                        <img src="/images/ERNC/ERNC_BannerCard/card-icon-01.png" alt="">
                    </div>
                    <div class="IconBlock-Text">Stake</div>
                </div>

                <div class="Card-Inner-Text">Users can seal their currency to participate in the newly discovered ERNC.
                    At the same
                    time, they may enhance their own governance and share the game's profits.</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="Card-flex">
            <div class="Card-BG">
                <div class="Card-Inner">

                    <div class="IconBlock">
                        <div class="IconBlock-Img">
                            <img src="/images/ERNC/ERNC_BannerCard/card-icon-02.png" alt="">
                        </div>
                        <div class="IconBlock-Text">Payment</div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="Card-Inner-Text">ERNC would be used to pay for a variety of high-level productions in the
                        game, as well as to trade NFTs on the auction market or to swap to other crypto currencies.</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="Card-BG">
                <div class="Card-Inner">

                    <div class="IconBlock">
                        <div class="IconBlock-Img">
                            <img src="/images/ERNC/ERNC_BannerCard/card-icon-03.png" alt="">
                        </div>
                        <div class="IconBlock-Text">Governance</div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="Card-Inner-Text">85% of the earnings will go into the decentralized treasury, and whoever
                        stakes enough ERNC will gain governance authority, allowing them to control treasury distribution
                        and vote on resolutions.</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
